DarkMouse::
She returned to the room where Megatron was still sitting. She walked over 
to him and whispered,"Commander, I found listening devices and hidden 
survielance devises all over the ship. I don't like this at all.  I know 
your here to talk, but I'd rather we head back to our base and talk through 
the comm-link. I just got a bad feeling about all this."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Battera::
She sat opposite CyberShark in the dining hall.  "If you don't mind me 
asking, I was wondering how you came to be here at this base?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

KiKat::
She chuckled at Quickstrike and nodded in agreement. She watched the two 
bots play around, throwing mustard and drawing swords. She made a disgusted 
face when they hugged. She turned and faced Quickstrike. She leaned down 
again and whispered, "And Megatron let these two bots live?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Shadow Wing::
She flew up ahead and flew next to Prowl. "What is our next move? Are we 
going to fight back or wait until they attack us again.  I mean, after what 
they did to the Ark, shouldn't we do something?"
